5
00:00:19,280 --> 00:00:22,140
You can also hear this sound in words like

6
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,120
“take,”

7
00:00:23,340 --> 00:00:23,980
“day,”

8
00:00:24,360 --> 00:00:25,160
“wait”

9
00:00:25,380 --> 00:00:26,980
or “eight.”

10
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:33,600
We’ll be using a special phonetic symbol - /eɪ/ - for this sound.

11
